<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 21:14:42 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>随着芯片需求稳定，TI 季度利润超出预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/analog-chipmaker-ti-beats-second-quarter-profit-estimates-2024-07-23/</link><description>德州仪器 (TI) 周二第二季度利润超出了分析师的预期，原因是个人电子产品等市场对模拟芯片的需求在疫情期间因库存导致长达数年的供过于求之后趋于稳定。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 20:10:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/analog-chipmaker-ti-beats-second-quarter-profit-estimates-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>人工智能订单抵消了中国销售额下降后，ASMI 上调了季度指引</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asmi-raises-quarterly-guidance-after-ai-orders-offset-chinese-sales-drop-2024-07-23/</link><description>计算机芯片制造设备供应商 ASM 国际公司 (ASMI) 周二表示，由于人工智能相关产品抵消了中国销售额的下降，第二季度订单超出预期，该公司上调了第三季度指引。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 17:08:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asmi-raises-quarterly-guidance-after-ai-orders-offset-chinese-sales-drop-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>渔业条约在世贸组织失败引发中美担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/fishing-treaty-fails-wto-prompting-us-chinese-concern-2024-07-23/</link><description>周二，削减渔业补贴的条约草案未能通过后，各国和环保组织表达了担忧和失望，中国呼吁各国对世界贸易组织的谈判方式进行重大改变。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 16:54:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/fishing-treaty-fails-wto-prompting-us-chinese-concern-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>据《Information》报道，苹果最早可能会在 2026 年发布可折叠 iPhone</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-likely-release-foldable-iphone-early-2026-information-reports-2024-07-23/</link><description>据周二报道，苹果公司可能最早在 2026 年推出可折叠 iPhone，这可能标志着该公司最受欢迎产品的最大硬件设计改造。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 16:53:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-likely-release-foldable-iphone-early-2026-information-reports-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国市场放缓，路威酩轩集团销售额未达预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/lvmh-sales-grow-1-second-quarter-2024-07-23/</link><description>尽管西方市场的需求略有回升，但由于中国消费者控制了国内高端时装的支出，路威酩轩第二季度的销售增长放缓。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 15:59:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/lvmh-sales-grow-1-second-quarter-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>联合国驻也门特使表示，胡塞武装对红海航运的威胁正在加剧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/houthi-threat-red-sea-shipping-is-growing-says-un-envoy-yemen-2024-07-23/</link><description>联合国驻也门特使汉斯·格伦德伯格周二向联合国安理会表示，红海及周边水道的最新事态发展表明，也门胡塞武装对国际航运的威胁正在加剧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 15:17:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/houthi-threat-red-sea-shipping-is-growing-says-un-envoy-yemen-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰外长抵达中国讨论“公平和平”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/ukraines-foreign-minister-arrives-china-discuss-fair-peace-2024-07-23/</link><description>乌克兰外长周二抵达中国，与外交部长王毅举行会谈，讨论如何在与俄罗斯的战争中实现“公平和平”，并讨论双边关系。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 14:27:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/ukraines-foreign-minister-arrives-china-discuss-fair-peace-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国在兴奋剂纠纷中向美国挑战金牌炫耀权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/china-challenge-us-gold-medal-bragging-rights-amid-doping-rout-2024-07-23/</link><description>中国来到巴黎奥运会，期待着近几十年来亚洲体育强国屡见不鲜的金牌潮，但兴奋剂纠纷的阴影却笼罩着代表团。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 13:20:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/china-challenge-us-gold-medal-bragging-rights-amid-doping-rout-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车在中国举步维艰。电动汽车能否帮助其在美国发展？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-is-reeling-china-can-evs-help-it-grow-us-2024-07-23-2/</link><description>当大众集团上个月向美国电动卡车和 SUV 制造商 Rivian 投资 50 亿美元时，这家初创公司的股价因现金注入而飙升。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 12:59:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-is-reeling-china-can-evs-help-it-grow-us-2024-07-23-2/</guid></item><item><title>印度财政部长支持增加中国直接投资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/indias-finance-minister-backs-increasing-chinese-direct-investment-2024-07-23/</link><description>自2020年以来，新德里与北京关系日益紧张，导致资金流动受到干扰，印度财政部长支持其经济顾问的建议，允许更多中国投资进入该国。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 12:20:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/indias-finance-minister-backs-increasing-chinese-direct-investment-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国电动卡车初创公司 Windrose 将在美国 IPO 前筹集 2 亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-electric-truck-startup-windrose-raise-200-mln-before-us-ipo-source-says-2024-07-23/</link><description>一位直接知情人士透露，中国电动卡车初创公司 Windrose 计划在最后一轮股权投资和债务融资中筹集 2 亿美元，然后再寻求在美国进行首次公开​​募股。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 11:17:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-electric-truck-startup-windrose-raise-200-mln-before-us-ipo-source-says-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>厄瓜多尔海军准备打击加拉帕戈斯群岛周围的非法捕鱼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/ecuadors-navy-ready-combat-illegal-fishing-around-galapagos-islands-2024-07-23/</link><description>厄瓜多尔海军在与邻国盟友进行训练演习后，准备保护加拉帕戈斯群岛周围海域免受外国船只的非法捕鱼，这些船只每年都会到访，威胁该群岛水域的海洋野生动物。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 11:01:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/ecuadors-navy-ready-combat-illegal-fishing-around-galapagos-islands-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>通用汽车超出季度预期并上调预测，但股价跳水</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/gm-beats-second-quarter-expectations-raises-forecast-again-2024-07-23/</link><description>通用汽车周二公布的第二季度利润和收入超出了华尔街的预期，并在强劲的定价和汽油动力卡车需求的推动下，今年第二次上调了年度利润预期。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 10:31:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/gm-beats-second-quarter-expectations-raises-forecast-again-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：巨型股报告，哈里斯在框架内，中国摇摆不定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-07-23/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 10:17:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>五角大楼表达担忧后，克里姆林宫表示俄罗斯与中国的北极合作不针对任何人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/kremlin-says-russian-arctic-cooperation-with-china-is-not-aimed-against-anyone-2024-07-23/</link><description>克里姆林宫周二表示，俄罗斯与中国在北极的合作并不针对任何其他国家，并表示美国对此类工作的批评是错误的。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 09:53:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/kremlin-says-russian-arctic-cooperation-with-china-is-not-aimed-against-anyone-2024-07-23/</guid></item></channel></rss>